    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "平日とはいえ、夏休み期間ですからね\nこの時期に人が来なけりゃ、海は商売あがったりです",
      "startTime": 104.0666631062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.6284511489
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "……ところで、私に遊んでこいとはおっしゃいましたが\nなんで、まだ{user}さんがいるんです",
      "startTime": 111.7938516454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "ロケ地の調査は終わったのですから\nホテルに戻って、明日の準備をしてはいかがですか",
      "startTime": 117.4938516454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
