      "text": "（mihoさんを一人で放り出す訳にはいかない）\n（……と言うと、多分また嫌がるだろうし）",
      "startTime": 124.3878334073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.9113760873
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いや、俺も少しくらい海を満喫しようと思いまして……",
      "startTime": 127.9113760873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "人に、遊べだのなんだのと言っておいて\n結局、自分が海で遊びたかっただけじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 135.4124913371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
