      "text": "まぁ……実地調査をお手伝いいただきましたし",
      "startTime": 138.8347318891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.2087001883
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "今回だけは、マネージャーが業務時間中に遊んでいても\n見逃して差し上げますけど",
      "startTime": 146.9697774377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.2617613558
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "はは、ありがとうございます……\n口止め料として、そこの海の家で昼飯を奢りますよ",
      "startTime": 152.4466095787,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
